location.fullValue: Legacy 3040 Plan, Parks at Glen Ridge

data.description: WELCOME HOME to this stunning 5 bedroom, 3 full bathroom residence nestled in Franklin Township. Enjoy the convenience of a main-level bedroom w/full bath. This home overlooks a tranquil pond with fountain, and complemented by a spacious fenced backyard perfect for your outdoor gatherings. With a 3 car garage providing ample storage, this home boasts new paint throughout and fresh carpeting upstairs and in the office as well. Retreat to the comfort of walk in closets in the bedrooms, while the upstairs laundry offers convenience with direct access to the Master Suite. Experience the epitome of luxury living in this meticulously crafted abode. Also, being on a court provides a quiet street for the kids to ride their bikes and scooters.
